{
  "video_id": "Fr26scqsIwk",
  "title": "It's time to re-evaluate our relationship with animals: Lesli Bisgould at TEDxUofT",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 3437.0,
      "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 10330.0,
      "end_time": 12800.0,
      "text": "I want to begin by making two statements, one at a time."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 12800.0,
      "end_time": 14300.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m going to ask you all, if you"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 14300.0,
      "end_time": 16590.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t mind, to raise your hand if you agree."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 16590.0,
      "end_time": 17620.0,
      "text": "So here&#39;s the first one."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 17620.0,
      "end_time": 18760.0,
      "text": "Ready?"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 18760.0,
      "end_time": 21992.0,
      "text": "Animals should be treated humanely."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 21992.0,
      "end_time": 24450.0,
      "text": "I can barely see, but it looks like lots of hands going up."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 24450.0,
      "end_time": 25250.0,
      "text": "OK, thanks."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 25250.0,
      "end_time": 26416.0,
      "text": "You can put your hands down."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 26416.0,
      "end_time": 27380.0,
      "text": "Here is the second one."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 27380.0,
      "end_time": 31970.0,
      "text": "Animals should not be made to suffer unnecessarily."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 31970.0,
      "end_time": 32740.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 32740.000000000004,
      "end_time": 34970.0,
      "text": "Seems like most people agree."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 34970.0,
      "end_time": 38200.0,
      "text": "And I would bet that if I ventured outside and put"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 38200.0,
      "end_time": 40319.0,
      "text": "those statements to passersby, I would likely"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 40319.0,
      "end_time": 42110.0,
      "text": "find that most people out there agree, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 42110.0,
      "end_time": 43890.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not really surprising, is it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 47300.0,
      "end_time": 49650.0,
      "text": "More than half of the households in North America"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 49650.0,
      "end_time": 51930.0,
      "text": "have companion animals, and most of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 51930.0,
      "end_time": 54430.0,
      "text": "are very upset when we hear the occasional story in the news"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 54430.0,
      "end_time": 56540.0,
      "text": "about some horrible act that&#39;s been done"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 56540.0,
      "end_time": 59410.0,
      "text": "to a dog or a cat or other animal."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 59410.0,
      "end_time": 61560.0,
      "text": "And the law codifies this perspective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 61560.0,
      "end_time": 64530.0,
      "text": "which is to say that virtually every jurisdiction in North"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 64530.0,
      "end_time": 67190.0,
      "text": "America has laws that say animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 67190.0,
      "end_time": 68800.0,
      "text": "should be treated humanely."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 68800.0,
      "end_time": 71820.0,
      "text": "Animals should not be made to suffer unnecessarily."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 71820.0,
      "end_time": 74280.0,
      "text": "And those laws are useless."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 74280.0,
      "end_time": 76590.0,
      "text": "They do nothing, and they in no way"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 76590.0,
      "end_time": 79630.0,
      "text": "protect animals from human-caused suffering"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 79630.0,
      "end_time": 82130.0,
      "text": "in any meaningful way, I should say."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 82130.0,
      "end_time": 85000.0,
      "text": "So I thought I would talk about is why that&#39;s the case"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 85000.0,
      "end_time": 87000.0,
      "text": "and why it&#39;s time to reevaluate our relationship"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 87000.0,
      "end_time": 89770.0,
      "text": "with other animals and the emerging field of animal rights"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 89770.0,
      "end_time": 92170.0,
      "text": "law that is doing just that."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 92170.0,
      "end_time": 94000.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s say that I wasn&#39;t really"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 94000.0,
      "end_time": 96380.0,
      "text": "here because I cared about doing this talk"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 96380.0,
      "end_time": 99890.0,
      "text": "but because my child has a heart problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 99890.0,
      "end_time": 102700.0,
      "text": "and is in need of a transplant to save her life."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 102700.0,
      "end_time": 104520.0,
      "text": "And I wanted access to a large group"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 104520.0,
      "end_time": 106740.0,
      "text": "of people whom I could discreetly look over"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 106740.0,
      "end_time": 109630.0,
      "text": "while I was doing this talk to see who among you looks"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 109630.0,
      "end_time": 111400.0,
      "text": "nice and healthy and strong."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 111400.0,
      "end_time": 115270.0,
      "text": "And when this event ends, I were to kidnap one of you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 115270.0,
      "end_time": 116940.0,
      "text": "whisk you away to a secret surgery"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 116940.0,
      "end_time": 119876.0,
      "text": "where I could remove your heart to be donated to my child."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 119876.0,
      "end_time": 120750.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s noting personal."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 120750.0,
      "end_time": 123930.0,
      "text": "You all seem very nice, but I don&#39;t love you"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 123930.0,
      "end_time": 126070.0,
      "text": "as much as I love my child, and your heart"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 126070.0,
      "end_time": 128880.0,
      "text": "is necessary for her survival."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 128880.0,
      "end_time": 132410.0,
      "text": "Would that be morally or legally justifiable?"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 132410.0,
      "end_time": 133420.0,
      "text": "Certainly not."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 133420.0,
      "end_time": 134670.0,
      "text": "Well, you&#39;re using your heart."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 134670.0,
      "end_time": 137270.0,
      "text": "No other person can claim any moral or legal right to it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 137270.0,
      "end_time": 139700.0,
      "text": "no matter how compelling the reason."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 139700.0,
      "end_time": 143430.0,
      "text": "Among legal equals, it&#39;s absurd to use the word &quot;necessary&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 143430.0,
      "end_time": 146040.0,
      "text": "in this context, and we just don&#39;t do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 146040.0,
      "end_time": 148120.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s different when it comes to animals."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 148120.0,
      "end_time": 151010.0,
      "text": "When we see that laws protect animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 151010.0,
      "end_time": 154250.0,
      "text": "from unnecessary suffering, they seem superficially impressive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 154250.0,
      "end_time": 156304.0,
      "text": "but it doesn&#39;t take long, and you"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 156304.0,
      "end_time": 157970.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t have to be a lawyer, to figure out"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 157970.0,
      "end_time": 161830.0,
      "text": "that, if the law prohibits causing unnecessary suffering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 161830.0,
      "end_time": 165170.0,
      "text": "it creates a corollary, meaning it permits"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 165170.0,
      "end_time": 167840.0,
      "text": "us to cause necessary suffering."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 167840.0,
      "end_time": 169280.0,
      "text": "What is necessary suffering?"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 169280.0,
      "end_time": 171450.0,
      "text": "Well, we write the laws."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 171450.0,
      "end_time": 172420.0,
      "text": "We enforce the laws."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 172420.0,
      "end_time": 173680.0,
      "text": "We interpret them."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 173680.0,
      "end_time": 175560.0,
      "text": "Turns out, it&#39;s necessary for an animal"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 175560.0,
      "end_time": 179200.0,
      "text": "to suffer whenever we say so."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 179200.0,
      "end_time": 183890.0,
      "text": "So our laws prohibit gratuitous suffering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 183890.0,
      "end_time": 185810.0,
      "text": "the kind that&#39;s caused sheerly by what"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 185810.0,
      "end_time": 187582.0,
      "text": "we might call wicked intent."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 187582.0,
      "end_time": 189790.0,
      "text": "But as soon as there&#39;s a human purpose-- and, really,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 189790.0,
      "end_time": 192810.0,
      "text": "almost any purpose will do-- that suffering"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 192810.0,
      "end_time": 195550.0,
      "text": "is necessary and protected."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 195550.0,
      "end_time": 198480.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s been that way for a really long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 198480.0,
      "end_time": 200355.0,
      "text": "Remember philosopher John Locke?"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 200355.0,
      "end_time": 202670.0,
      "text": "Can you think back to the 17th century?"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 202670.0,
      "end_time": 204890.0,
      "text": "So he conceived of the notions of property"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 204890.0,
      "end_time": 207160.0,
      "text": "that are now central to our legal system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 207160.0,
      "end_time": 209450.0,
      "text": "in part because he was trying to find a way"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 209450.0,
      "end_time": 212130.0,
      "text": "to allocate competing human interests in animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 212130.0,
      "end_time": 215660.0,
      "text": "and other natural resources in a principled way."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 215660.0,
      "end_time": 217160.0,
      "text": "And, of course, back then, nobody"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 217160.0,
      "end_time": 219450.0,
      "text": "thought of animal interests as one of those principles"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 219450.0,
      "end_time": 221380.0,
      "text": "to consider."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 221380.0,
      "end_time": 225950.0,
      "text": "So in a system of laws that grew to esteem property rights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 225950.0,
      "end_time": 231660.0,
      "text": "animals became property, and humans became property owners."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 231660.0,
      "end_time": 233472.0,
      "text": "And so it remains."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 233472.0,
      "end_time": 235320.0,
      "text": "And a central role of property is"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 235320.0,
      "end_time": 238944.0,
      "text": "that an owner can use her thing however she sees fit."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 238944.0,
      "end_time": 240860.0,
      "text": "She can do whatever she wants with her things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 240860.0,
      "end_time": 245020.0,
      "text": "so long as she doesn&#39;t use that thing to hurt somebody else."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 245020.0,
      "end_time": 248140.0,
      "text": "But the thing itself has no rights."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 248140.0,
      "end_time": 251530.0,
      "text": "So this idea that animals are things that serve our purposes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 251530.0,
      "end_time": 254750.0,
      "text": "that they are our property, have been really powerful."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 254750.0,
      "end_time": 256279.0,
      "text": "It has entrenched."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 256279.0,
      "end_time": 259879.0,
      "text": "And it now facilitates the systematic suffering"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 259879.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263880.00000000006,
      "text": "of billions-- with a B-- of animals every year"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 263880.0,
      "end_time": 267390.0,
      "text": "in North America in a variety of industries."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 267390.0,
      "end_time": 269320.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m going to give you just one example."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 269320.0,
      "end_time": 271550.0,
      "text": "In the Canadian agriculture industry alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 271550.0,
      "end_time": 278390.0,
      "text": "every year, 700 million animals are intensively confined,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 278390.0,
      "end_time": 281470.0,
      "text": "are mutilated in a variety of very painful procedures"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 281470.0,
      "end_time": 282875.0,
      "text": "without anesthetic."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 282875.0,
      "end_time": 285390.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re living in their own waste."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 285390.0,
      "end_time": 287620.0,
      "text": "Many of them are sick and diseased"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 287620.0,
      "end_time": 290410.0,
      "text": "with broken bones and open wounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 290410.0,
      "end_time": 292680.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re beaten, electrocuted."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 292680.0,
      "end_time": 296010.0,
      "text": "When you see them traveling in those trucks on the highway"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 296010.0,
      "end_time": 298174.0,
      "text": "on the way to slaughter, for many of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 298174.0,
      "end_time": 299590.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s the first time they&#39;ve ever"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 299590.0,
      "end_time": 301590.0,
      "text": "been outside in their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 301590.0,
      "end_time": 304150.0,
      "text": "And they&#39;re so depleted that several million of them"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 304150.0,
      "end_time": 309490.0,
      "text": "arrive every year at the slaughterhouse already dead."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 309490.0,
      "end_time": 311640.0,
      "text": "Then there&#39;s research and fashion"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 311640.0,
      "end_time": 313505.0,
      "text": "and entertainment and sports."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 316090.0,
      "end_time": 318150.0,
      "text": "So for every story that we hear in the news"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 318150.0,
      "end_time": 320010.0,
      "text": "about some terrible act of violence"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 320010.0,
      "end_time": 322530.0,
      "text": "having been done to an individual animal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 322530.0,
      "end_time": 325130.0,
      "text": "there is an industrial counterpart"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 325130.0,
      "end_time": 328280.0,
      "text": "where that violence is normalized and multiply"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 328280.0,
      "end_time": 332200.0,
      "text": "by hundreds or thousands or millions of times."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 332200.0,
      "end_time": 334520.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s the institutional imperative"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 334520.0,
      "end_time": 337170.0,
      "text": "that is such a big problem for animals today."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 337170.0,
      "end_time": 339540.0,
      "text": "And Chomsky has discussed this in other contexts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 339540.0,
      "end_time": 342880.0,
      "text": "how even really good people can do really bad things when"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 342880.0,
      "end_time": 345410.0,
      "text": "institutions demand it."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 345410.0,
      "end_time": 347890.0,
      "text": "So in the animal context, industry"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 347890.0,
      "end_time": 351060.0,
      "text": "has embedded practices that would be considered monstrous"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 351060.0,
      "end_time": 353280.0,
      "text": "if they were done to our own pet dog,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 353280.0,
      "end_time": 355650.0,
      "text": "even if sometimes those practices are carried out"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 355650.0,
      "end_time": 357710.0,
      "text": "by people who love their own dogs"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 357710.0,
      "end_time": 361597.0,
      "text": "and are otherwise kind and admirable people."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 361597.0,
      "end_time": 363180.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why another part of the problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 363180.0,
      "end_time": 365130.0,
      "text": "is the laws focused on cruelty to animals."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 365130.0,
      "end_time": 367650.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s always how you hear a wrong described, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 367650.0,
      "end_time": 375140.0,
      "text": "When you want to object to something done to an animal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 375140.0,
      "end_time": 377100.0,
      "text": "you say it&#39;s cruel."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 377100.0,
      "end_time": 380020.0,
      "text": "But cruelty is the wrong word, because it connotes"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 380020.0,
      "end_time": 382130.0,
      "text": "a malevolent intent, doesn&#39;t it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 382130.0,
      "end_time": 383940.0,
      "text": "Causing harm for harm&#39;s sake."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 383940.0,
      "end_time": 385650.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s really the case."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 385650.0,
      "end_time": 387940.0,
      "text": "The people who engage in this institutional violence"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 387940.0,
      "end_time": 392510.0,
      "text": "may be desensitized or profit driven or desperate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 392510.0,
      "end_time": 394960.0,
      "text": "as in the case of some agricultural workers."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 394960.0,
      "end_time": 398380.0,
      "text": "But they&#39;re really motivated sheerly by wicked intent."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 398380.0,
      "end_time": 402164.0,
      "text": "In fact, in some cases, the intent can be quite noble."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 402164.0,
      "end_time": 403830.0,
      "text": "Imagine two people coming home from work"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 403830.0,
      "end_time": 405344.0,
      "text": "at the end of the day."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 405344.0,
      "end_time": 406635.0,
      "text": "One of them had a horrible day."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 406635.0,
      "end_time": 409964.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s in a terrible mood, and his dog will not stop barking."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 409964.0,
      "end_time": 412950.0,
      "text": "He has a blow torch in the garage."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 412950.0,
      "end_time": 415210.0,
      "text": "So he restrains his dog on her leash,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 415210.0,
      "end_time": 417190.0,
      "text": "goes out and gets the blow torch,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 417190.0,
      "end_time": 419970.0,
      "text": "comes back and burns the dog."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 419970.0,
      "end_time": 422840.0,
      "text": "Second person is a researcher, and she&#39;s presently"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 422840.0,
      "end_time": 426420.0,
      "text": "engaged in the study about the efficacy of various treatments"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 426420.0,
      "end_time": 427512.0,
      "text": "on burns."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 427512.0,
      "end_time": 429970.0,
      "text": "And she&#39;s returning home from a day at the laboratory where"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 429970.0,
      "end_time": 433530.0,
      "text": "she has restrained several dogs and blow torched them"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 433530.0,
      "end_time": 435860.0,
      "text": "in pursuit of her study."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 435860.0,
      "end_time": 440644.0,
      "text": "First person had no real purpose for burning his dog that way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 440644.0,
      "end_time": 443060.0,
      "text": "and he might be charged with causing unnecessary suffering"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 443060.0,
      "end_time": 443560.0,
      "text": "to the dog."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 443560.0,
      "end_time": 446720.0,
      "text": "But the second person not only won&#39;t be charged."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 446720.0,
      "end_time": 450310.0,
      "text": "She will be protected by her institution, supported"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 450310.0,
      "end_time": 452040.0,
      "text": "with public tax dollars, rewarded"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 452040.0,
      "end_time": 455350.0,
      "text": "with professional recognition if her results get published."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 455350.0,
      "end_time": 458740.0,
      "text": "And the rest of us, if we ever hear about such things at all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 458740.0,
      "end_time": 462090.0,
      "text": "will be assured that the experiment was humane,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 462090.0,
      "end_time": 464200.0,
      "text": "just as we are assured by agriculture industry"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 464200.0,
      "end_time": 466870.0,
      "text": "spokespeople that all the things I described a moment ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 466870.0,
      "end_time": 469190.0,
      "text": "are humane, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 469190.0,
      "end_time": 471580.0,
      "text": "So when industry gives us these assurances,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 471580.0,
      "end_time": 473690.0,
      "text": "we do well to ask ourselves, what"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 473690.0,
      "end_time": 477250.0,
      "text": "is their interest in having us believe that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 477250.0,
      "end_time": 481090.0,
      "text": "And we do well to consider the industry itself writes"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 481090.0,
      "end_time": 483210.0,
      "text": "the voluntary codes of practice that"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 483210.0,
      "end_time": 486020.0,
      "text": "govern most animals in industrial use,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 486020.0,
      "end_time": 488120.0,
      "text": "that there&#39;s hardly any government oversight."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 490850.0,
      "end_time": 492680.0,
      "text": "I became involved in animal rights"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 492680.0,
      "end_time": 497460.0,
      "text": "when I came across an image that disturbed me."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 497460.0,
      "end_time": 499520.0,
      "text": "And you know how it is once you see things."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 499520.0,
      "end_time": 502040.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no unseeing them."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 502040.0,
      "end_time": 504290.0,
      "text": "So I felt compelled to learn more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 504290.0,
      "end_time": 507220.0,
      "text": "and I learned how a cow becomes a steak"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 507220.0,
      "end_time": 509770.0,
      "text": "and how an elephant becomes a circus performer"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 509770.0,
      "end_time": 514409.0,
      "text": "and how a coyote becomes the trim on the hood of a coat."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 514409.0,
      "end_time": 516280.0,
      "text": "Those images are not offered to us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 516280.0,
      "end_time": 519250.0,
      "text": "and those responsible for them to go to great lengths"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 519250.0,
      "end_time": 522230.0,
      "text": "to keep them from us, but they are there for the finding."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 522230.0,
      "end_time": 526705.0,
      "text": "And unless &quot;humane&quot; means horrible and profitable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 526705.0,
      "end_time": 530140.0,
      "text": "there is nothing humane in those images."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 530140.0,
      "end_time": 533550.0,
      "text": "And nor are those images the result of a few rotten apples,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 533550.0,
      "end_time": 536590.0,
      "text": "which is the next assurance industry"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 536590.0,
      "end_time": 539990.0,
      "text": "gives us on the occasions when their practices are exposed."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 539990.0,
      "end_time": 543420.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the normal, routine practices of exploitation"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 543420.0,
      "end_time": 546066.0,
      "text": "that are rotten."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 546066.0,
      "end_time": 547940.0,
      "text": "So this has all been very brief, but hang in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 547940.0,
      "end_time": 552560.0,
      "text": "because this brings to the new dimensions part of this talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 552560.0,
      "end_time": 556680.0,
      "text": "You see, we don&#39;t treat animals badly because they&#39;re property."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 556680.0,
      "end_time": 558640.0,
      "text": "We classify animals as property so"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 558640.0,
      "end_time": 559880.0,
      "text": "that we can treat them badly."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 559880.0,
      "end_time": 561222.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t have to."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 561222.0,
      "end_time": 561930.0,
      "text": "We can do better."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 561930.0,
      "end_time": 563740.0,
      "text": "We can classify them differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 563740.0,
      "end_time": 565160.0,
      "text": "And the moral imperative to do so"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 565160.0,
      "end_time": 569330.0,
      "text": "has been pressing for 150 years, since Darwin revolutionized"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 569330.0,
      "end_time": 572210.0,
      "text": "our understanding about our place in the animal world"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 572210.0,
      "end_time": 575510.0,
      "text": "with his theory of evolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 575510.0,
      "end_time": 577990.0,
      "text": "Darwin explained that you are all a bunch of animals."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 577990.0,
      "end_time": 581360.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re all animals, more or less closely related to one another"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 581360.0,
      "end_time": 583760.0,
      "text": "by virtue of our descent from different ancestors"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 583760.0,
      "end_time": 586800.0,
      "text": "or from common ancestors, and that animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 586800.0,
      "end_time": 592410.0,
      "text": "differ from one another in degree, but not in kind."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 592410.0,
      "end_time": 595120.0,
      "text": "And this was revolutionary, because we&#39;ve traditionally"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 595120.0,
      "end_time": 596840.0,
      "text": "justified the differential treatment"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 596840.0,
      "end_time": 598470.0,
      "text": "that we give to animals on the basis"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 598470.0,
      "end_time": 601790.0,
      "text": "of some assumed categorical differences between us"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 601790.0,
      "end_time": 602720.0,
      "text": "and them."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 602720.0,
      "end_time": 603810.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t think."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 603810.0,
      "end_time": 604630.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t feel."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 604630.0,
      "end_time": 606432.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t communicate."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 606432.0,
      "end_time": 609220.0,
      "text": "But Darwin discredited those assumptions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 609220.0,
      "end_time": 611220.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;ve been discredited much further still"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 611220.0,
      "end_time": 613710.0,
      "text": "by various branches of natural science"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 613710.0,
      "end_time": 616360.0,
      "text": "and applied science in the 15 decades since."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 616360.0,
      "end_time": 619395.0,
      "text": "And our laws have lost their factual premise."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 622320.0,
      "end_time": 625830.0,
      "text": "So the moral implications of this evolution revolution"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 625830.0,
      "end_time": 627450.0,
      "text": "have taken a long time to sink in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 627450.0,
      "end_time": 631190.0,
      "text": "but no serious thinker disputes anymore that animals think"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 631190.0,
      "end_time": 633200.0,
      "text": "and feel and communicate, that they"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 633200.0,
      "end_time": 635840.0,
      "text": "are the subjects of a life."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 635840.0,
      "end_time": 637840.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re starting to appreciate that animal life is"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 637840.0,
      "end_time": 640570.0,
      "text": "much more like a web than the pyramid we&#39;ve"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 640570.0,
      "end_time": 645690.0,
      "text": "been used to drawing, that they are literally our kin."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 645690.0,
      "end_time": 647414.0,
      "text": "Now, there are differences between humans"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 647414.0,
      "end_time": 648830.0,
      "text": "and other animals, of course, just"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 648830.0,
      "end_time": 650920.0,
      "text": "as there are differences between humans."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 650920.0,
      "end_time": 652800.0,
      "text": "We have this notion of human quality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 652800.0,
      "end_time": 654500.0,
      "text": "but that&#39;s not because we&#39;re actually"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 654500.0,
      "end_time": 657655.0,
      "text": "equal in our capacities or abilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 657655.0,
      "end_time": 658280.0,
      "text": "Think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 658280.0,
      "end_time": 660846.0,
      "text": "Some people are taller than others."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 660846.0,
      "end_time": 662220.0,
      "text": "Some people are more intelligent."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 662220.0,
      "end_time": 665370.0,
      "text": "Some people have nicer dispositions."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 665370.0,
      "end_time": 670050.0,
      "text": "We have different genders and disabilities and religions."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 670050.0,
      "end_time": 671920.0,
      "text": "Some people can compose operas."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 671920.0,
      "end_time": 673190.0,
      "text": "Some can&#39;t sing a note."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 673190.0,
      "end_time": 676480.0,
      "text": "Some can win Olympic medals in hockey."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 676480.0,
      "end_time": 678290.0,
      "text": "Some can&#39;t skate."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 678290.0,
      "end_time": 680480.0,
      "text": "So we have many differences, but we"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 680480.0,
      "end_time": 683370.0,
      "text": "have decided that none of those differences"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 683370.0,
      "end_time": 685270.0,
      "text": "is morally relevant when it comes"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 685270.0,
      "end_time": 688570.0,
      "text": "to protecting our fundamental interests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 688570.0,
      "end_time": 691157.0,
      "text": "like our interests in living our own lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 691157.0,
      "end_time": 693115.0,
      "text": "and not being hurt for somebody else&#39;s purpose."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 696080.0,
      "end_time": 698190.0,
      "text": "In another talk, we might explore"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 698190.0,
      "end_time": 700130.0,
      "text": "whether human rights operate more in theory"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 700130.0,
      "end_time": 704800.0,
      "text": "than in practice, but at least we are working on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 704800.0,
      "end_time": 705710.0,
      "text": "We are working on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 705710.0,
      "end_time": 707793.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s where animal rights theory comes along."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 707793.0,
      "end_time": 710186.0,
      "text": "It asks us to confront this question."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 710186.0,
      "end_time": 712420.0,
      "text": "What are the morally irrelevant differences"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 712420.0,
      "end_time": 715520.0,
      "text": "between humans and other animals that make it"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 715520.0,
      "end_time": 718820.0,
      "text": "acceptable for us to hurt them in ways that would never"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 718820.0,
      "end_time": 722380.0,
      "text": "be acceptable to hurt one another?"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 722380.0,
      "end_time": 723880.0,
      "text": "So as we wrestle with this question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 723880.0,
      "end_time": 726480.0,
      "text": "the lack of a comfortable answer is propelling the development"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 726480.0,
      "end_time": 728910.0,
      "text": "of animal rights law, where we try"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 728910.0,
      "end_time": 731370.0,
      "text": "to generate legal rights for animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 731370.0,
      "end_time": 733710.0,
      "text": "by eroding their property status."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 733710.0,
      "end_time": 738620.0,
      "text": "You can think of a right as a barrier that exists between you"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 738620.0,
      "end_time": 740720.0,
      "text": "and everybody who stands to benefit"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 740720.0,
      "end_time": 742798.0,
      "text": "by hurting or exploiting them."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 742798.0,
      "end_time": 744256.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s what stands between me and you"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 744256.0,
      "end_time": 748520.0,
      "text": "and stops me from taking your heart for someone I love more."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 748520.0,
      "end_time": 751040.0,
      "text": "So in animal rights law, we&#39;re not"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 751040.0,
      "end_time": 753980.0,
      "text": "trying to extend human rights to animals, as you sometimes hear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 753980.0,
      "end_time": 754480.0,
      "text": "right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 754480.0,
      "end_time": 756450.0,
      "text": "Nobody thinks animals should have the right"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 756450.0,
      "end_time": 760950.0,
      "text": "to vote or get married or have a good education."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 760950.0,
      "end_time": 763720.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s really about establishing the right"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 763720.0,
      "end_time": 766810.0,
      "text": "to have their fundamental interests respected"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 766810.0,
      "end_time": 770210.0,
      "text": "when we consider taking actions that will affect them."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 770210.0,
      "end_time": 773600.0,
      "text": "And that could mean changing their status from property"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 773600.0,
      "end_time": 775950.0,
      "text": "to legal person."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 775950.0,
      "end_time": 779210.0,
      "text": "And if it seems strange to think of an animal as a legal person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 779210.0,
      "end_time": 783650.0,
      "text": "consider that a whole array of inanimate constructs--"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 783650.0,
      "end_time": 788150.0,
      "text": "corporations, churches, trusts, municipalities--"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 788150.0,
      "end_time": 791800.0,
      "text": "are all legal persons in that they have legally protected"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 791800.0,
      "end_time": 794522.0,
      "text": "interests, and they can go to court and advance them."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 794522.0,
      "end_time": 797520.0,
      "text": "And animals are the only sentient beings who aren&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 800470.0,
      "end_time": 805380.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s a long road to peaceful coexistence between humans"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 805380.0,
      "end_time": 808490.0,
      "text": "and other animals, and that is partly"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 808490.0,
      "end_time": 812350.0,
      "text": "because, even though all of us say we don&#39;t want animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 812350.0,
      "end_time": 817350.0,
      "text": "to suffer unnecessarily, most of us wittingly or unwittingly"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 817350.0,
      "end_time": 819190.0,
      "text": "to some degree are users of animals"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 819190.0,
      "end_time": 821630.0,
      "text": "or consumers of their various bits and pieces."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 821630.0,
      "end_time": 824280.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;ve proved as a whole pretty reluctant"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 824280.0,
      "end_time": 826040.0,
      "text": "to give up all the privileges that"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 826040.0,
      "end_time": 829430.0,
      "text": "come with our superior legal status."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 829430.0,
      "end_time": 832435.0,
      "text": "But we&#39;re starting to see things differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 832435.0,
      "end_time": 834930.0,
      "text": "The animal rights movement is gaining credibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 834930.0,
      "end_time": 837680.0,
      "text": "and momentum, and laws are not fixed forever."
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 837680.0,
      "end_time": 840250.0,
      "text": "Law is a social institution that is meant to evolve over"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 840250.0,
      "end_time": 843660.0,
      "text": "time as hearts and minds change."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 843660.0,
      "end_time": 846440.0,
      "text": "So the law will begin to reflect our biological kinship"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 846440.0,
      "end_time": 851660.0,
      "text": "with other animals as soon as we decide we really want it to."
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 851660.0,
      "end_time": 852430.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 852430.0,
      "end_time": 856080.0,
      "text": "[APPLAUSE]"
    }
  ]
}